# Remarks

Net of discounts, returns, GST

Fulfillment costs to end customers and logistics costs between warehouses

FB, Google, others

Net of discounts, returns, GST

Avg commission is ~13%. Month of month variation is primarily due to timing difference due to late receipt of invoices

Higher logistics cost on account of 1) Higher closed footwear product mix; 2) Fulfillment largely done by Amazon from FY23

Net of discounts, returns, GST

Avg commission is ~12%. Month of month variation is primarily due to timing difference due to late receipt of invoices

Avg logistics cost is ~14%. Month of month variation is primarily due to timing difference due to late receipt of invoices

